@startuml
' @id(CMP-ARCH-CLI)
' @desc(CMP-ARCH-CLI, "The `mdd arch` CLI surface (nested diff/status subcommands in mdd-cli) plus the mdd-core architecture engine (architecture.rs: ArchitectureSpec parse, pure diff(), pure check(), and a thin git-show base reader). Distinct from CMP-ARCH-TRACKING (the spec artifact + templates + agent doc): this is the tooling that diffs and gates the spec. check() is also called by mdd validate.")
title Architecture CLI + engine (objective)

component "mdd arch (CLI)\nmdd-cli" as Cli
component "architecture.rs engine\n(parse / diff / check)" as Engine
component "mdd validate" as Validate
artifact ".mdd/architecture/*.yml" as Spec
component "git" as Git

Cli --> Engine : diff / status
Engine --> Spec : parse working
Engine --> Git : read base at ref (git show)
Validate --> Engine : check() as WARNING rules
@enduml
